Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Memory Long-Term Module Stub
Provides comprehensive long-term memory storage with indexing, consolidation, and schema evolution
Enables persistent memory management, storage optimization, and capacity management
:End Note

Type LongTermMemoryEntry is Dictionary with:
    entry_id as String
    content as Any
    entry_type as String
    importance as Float
    creation_time as Float
    last_accessed as Float
    access_count as Integer
    retention_level as String
    redundancy_level as Integer
    entry_metadata as Dictionary

Type LongTermStorage is Dictionary with:
    storage_id as String
    storage_name as String
    backend_type as String
    storage_config as Dictionary
    capacity_info as Dictionary
    performance_metrics as Dictionary
    storage_metadata as Dictionary

Type MemoryIndex is Dictionary with:
    index_id as String
    index_name as String
    index_type as String
    indexed_fields as List[String]
    index_structure as Dictionary
    index_metrics as Dictionary
    index_metadata as Dictionary

Type ConsolidationJob is Dictionary with:
    job_id as String
    source_entries as List[String]
    consolidation_strategy as String
    target_schema as String
    job_status as String
    job_metadata as Dictionary

Type StorageOperation is Dictionary with:
    operation_id as String
    operation_type as String
    operation_target as String
    operation_result as Dictionary
    operation_metadata as Dictionary

Type IndexQuery is Dictionary with:
    query_id as String
    query_type as String
    query_parameters as Dictionary
    query_filters as Dictionary
    query_metadata as Dictionary

Type SchemaEvolution is Dictionary with:
    evolution_id as String
    current_schema as String
    target_schema as String
    evolution_plan as Dictionary
    migration_scripts as List[String]
    evolution_metadata as Dictionary

Type StorageOptimization is Dictionary with:
    optimization_id as String
    optimization_type as String
    optimization_plan as Dictionary
    optimization_result as Dictionary
    optimization_metadata as Dictionary

Type CapacityManagement is Dictionary with:
    management_id as String
    management_policy as String
    capacity_analysis as Dictionary
    management_actions as List[Dictionary]
    management_metadata as Dictionary

Process called "create_long_term_memory_entry" that takes content as Any and entry_type as String and importance as Float returns LongTermMemoryEntry
Process called "store_memory_entry" that takes entry as LongTermMemoryEntry and storage as LongTermStorage returns Dictionary
Process called "retrieve_memory_entry" that takes entry_id as String and storage as LongTermStorage returns Dictionary
Process called "update_memory_entry" that takes entry_id as String and updates as Dictionary and storage as LongTermStorage returns Dictionary
Process called "delete_memory_entry" that takes entry_id as String and storage as LongTermStorage and deletion_policy as String returns Dictionary
Process called "create_memory_index" that takes index_name as String and index_type as String and fields as List[String] returns MemoryIndex
Process called "build_index" that takes index as MemoryIndex and entries as List[LongTermMemoryEntry] and storage as LongTermStorage returns Dictionary
Process called "query_memory_index" that takes index as MemoryIndex and query_params as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "optimize_index" that takes index as MemoryIndex returns Dictionary
Process called "consolidate_memories" that takes source_entries as List[String] and consolidation_strategy as String and storage as LongTermStorage returns ConsolidationJob
